  <h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">Who will train the pastors?</h1><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">The explosive growth of the church in Africa is exciting! But who will shepherd God’s rapidly growing flock? With false teaching and cults so prevalent, who will plant the churches, and teach, lead and care for God’s people? In a region with limited educational resources, where will Africa’s future pastors receive the training they need in Bible, Theology and Pastoral Ministry?</p>
